{"tid":1905581,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次嗌交就被冷戰","createTime":"2020-03-01T10:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T09:36:59.000Z","uid":26789,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f10d0ecd9470da08a1ec7db200b1ac4e495f398e","tid":1905581,"uid":26789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"一齊咗唔係好耐 半年左右<br />\n自問係脾氣都幾好嘅人<br />\n平時女朋友點發脾氣都好<br />\n我都冇嬲過佢 冇發佢脾氣 冇嗌過交<br />\n因為我知佢平時返工壓力好大<br />\n我體諒佢<br />\n<br />\n尋晚我第一次發佢脾氣 <br />\n算好聲好氣同佢講<br />\n講冇2句 佢就發返脾氣轉頭<br />\n結果佢就嗌晒分手咁<br />\n當時我都收一收 冇應到佢<br />\n只係叫佢夜啦瞓醒先講<br />\n因為我知佢當時情緒唔穩定<br />\n根本咩都聽唔入耳<br />\n<br />\n今日我都即刻認低威<br />\n結果換來以讀不回<br />\n被冷戰<br />\n究竟應該點做<br />\n<br />\n利申：年齡2個都20中"},{"pid":"b730e3a7f2704e42c92e7d1df12baf0d9241af54","tid":1905581,"uid":53466,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0aced599b51a627ce539caa5ce101b1aec65386a","tid":1905581,"uid":121229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"女人係咁"},{"pid":"951b8b2f7a689ea708353c1c52a2b8b81e7fcaaa","tid":1905581,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"買返個包包"},{"pid":"3ffffc64d1242a9035291c3d066e9299e3cc1f93","tid":1905581,"uid":139743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"你覺得你愛多啲定對方愛多啲"},{"pid":"17fb40edbd5295d73ccccdfbf3d0ae8ac88a5f0c","tid":1905581,"uid":26789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ffffc64d1242a9035291c3d066e9299e3cc1f93","tid":1905581,"uid":139743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"你覺得你愛多啲定對方愛多啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:05:27.000Z","msg":"我覺得我愛佢多啲"},{"pid":"53792ee08038e8147fddabf8d1ec380402a2f9f7","tid":1905581,"uid":26789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b730e3a7f2704e42c92e7d1df12baf0d9241af54","tid":1905581,"uid":53466,"like":8,"dislike":